Package: easyPLSDA
Type: Package
Title: easyPLSDA performs Partial Least Square regression for discriminant analysis purpose
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Jianhui Bi, Rudy Haziza and Luis VENTURA
Maintainer: Jianhui Bi <jianhui.bi@univ-lyon2.fr>, Rudy Haziza <rudy.haziza@univ-lyon2.fr> and Luis VENTURA <luis.ventura@univ-lyon2.fr>
Description: easyPLSDA performs Partial Least Square regression for discriminant analysis.The main function is easyPLSDA. This function create a plsDA S3 object with several attributes like scores, weights and loadings matrices.    easyPLSDA also use a automatic variable selection process (can be switched off) based on Variable Importance in Projection and can select automaticaly the optimal number of composantes.
